cs.CR, cs.LG, cs.NI, cs.CY, cs.SE

This paper is about defending against website fingerprinting attacks, which is a subfield of computer security (cs.CR). The paper leverages deep learning classifiers, which falls under the subfield of machine learning (cs.LG). The defense technique involves adding padding to traffic traces, which is related to network security (cs.NI) and cryptography (cs.CY). Finally, the paper proposes a novel defense technique, which is related to software engineering (cs.SE) as it involves developing and implementing a new algorithm.
